  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a \u0dc3\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Nishantha, President of Ceylon Estate Employees Union",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Nishantha Vanniarachchi has been elected as the President of Ceylon Estate Services Association.",
        "Mr. Nishantha Vanniarachchi was appointed as the chairman and Mr. Marimuttu Sudahar as the vice-chairmen of the 24th Biennial Conference of Ceylon Plantation Workers' Association held at the Western Province Beauty Resort under the theme \"A Century of Pride\". were elected",
        "Mr. Robert Fancis is the general secretary and S. for the General Assembly. L. Chandrapala, Chamara Premaratne, Hemantha Prasanna, S. John. Mahesh Ranasinghe and S. Mr. Tamilmaran was elected unopposed."
      ],
